---
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Story">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="story-hero">
        <!-- Napkin Background -->
        <div class="napkin-bg">
            <img src="/assets/images/napkin-architecture.jpg" alt="Original Fikanova architecture sketch" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-container">
            <span class="hero-location">Nairobi, 2025</span>
            <h1>It Started with a Napkin<br>and a <em>Belief.</em></h1>
            <p class="hero-lead">
                We looked at the Kenyan business landscape and saw a disconnect. While the world was racing toward autonomous intelligence, brilliant local businesses were still drowning in manual admin. We asked a simple question:
            </p>
            <blockquote>
                What if an SME could operate with the efficiency of a Fortune 500 company, without the headcount?
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Origin Section -->
    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="story-container">
            <span class="section-marker">01</span>
            <h2>The Meaning of <em>Fikanova</em></h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Our name is more than a label; it is a code for our process.</p>
            
            <div class="etymology">
                <div class="word-block">
                    <span class="word">Fikra</span>
                    <span class="origin">Swahili for "Idea"</span>
                    <p>The spark of human creativity that no machine can replicate.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="word-connector">+</div>
                <div class="word-block">
                    <span class="word">Arcane</span>
                    <span class="origin">Hidden Knowledge</span>
                    <p>The deep, often hidden technical knowledge required to control modern AI.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="word-connector">=</div>
                <div class="word-block highlight">
                    <span class="word">Nova</span>
                    <span class="origin">A Star Reborn</span>
                    <p>Bursting with new energy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="section-closing">
                We exist to be that collision point. To take your raw ideas, apply hidden technical leverage, and launch them into a new tier of performance.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Philosophy Section -->
    <section class="story-section alt">
        <div class="story-container">
            <span class="section-marker">02</span>
            <h2>The Physics of <em>Growth</em></h2>
            <p class="section-intro">We built Fikanova on a fundamental equation:</p>
            
            <div class="equation">
                <span class="eq-term">Wealth</span>
                <span class="eq-operator">=</span>
                <span class="eq-term">Time</span>
                <span class="eq-operator">×</span>
                <span class="eq-term">Knowledge</span>
            </div>
            
            <p>In the old economy, you had to trade time to build wealth. You hired more people to do more work. <strong>We believe that model is broken.</strong></p>
            
            <div class="principles">
                <div class="principle">
                    <Icon name="clock" size={16} />
                    <p><strong>Time</strong> should be reclaimed by automation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle">
                    <Icon name="cpu-chip" size={24} />
                    <p><strong>Knowledge</strong> should be embedded in systems that never forget.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle">
                    <Icon name="chart-bar" size={24} />
                    <p><strong>Wealth</strong> is the natural byproduct of efficiently managing the first two.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="section-closing">
                We don't just build websites; we build systems that manipulate this equation in your favor.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Hybrid Future Section -->
    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="story-container">
            <span class="section-marker">03</span>
            <h2>The "Human-in-the-Loop" <em>Promise</em></h2>
            <p class="section-intro">We are optimists, but we are not naive.</p>
            
            <p>We believe the future isn't "AI vs. Human"—it is <strong>"AI + Human."</strong></p>
            
            <blockquote>
                Technology without direction is chaos.
            </blockquote>
            
            <p>
                That is why we champion the <strong>Human Supervisor Model</strong>. We build the digital workforce (the agents, the bots, the code), but we design them to report to <em>you</em>.
            </p>
            
            <p class="section-closing highlight-text">
                You remain the pilot; we just build a faster plane.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Signoff Section -->
    <section class="story-signoff">
        <div class="story-container">
            <p class="signoff-tagline">Built in Nairobi. Deploying Globally.</p>
            <p class="signoff-statement">We are proud to be building the infrastructure of the African digital renaissance.</p>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <span class="signature-name">Nyaenya Moseti</span>
                <span class="signature-title">Founder, Fikanova</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Import Serif Font for Headings */
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600&display=swap');
    
    /* Story Container - Narrow for readability */
    .story-container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
    }
    
    /* Hero Section */
    .story-hero {
        position: relative;
        padding: 160px 0 80px;
        background: var(--dark-bg);
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    body.theme-light .story-hero {
        background: #faf8f5;
    }
    
    /* Napkin Background - Full Cover with Dark Overlay */
    .napkin-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .napkin-bg img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center;
        filter: sepia(30%) contrast(0.9) brightness(0.7);
    }
    
    .napkin-bg::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
    }
    
    .story-container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
    }
    
    /* Hero Text - White and Gold on dark background */
    .hero-location {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #c9a962 !important; /* Gold */
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .story-hero h1 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        color: #ffffff !important; /* White */
    }
    
    .story-hero h1 em {
        color: #c9a962 !important; /* Gold */
    }
    
    .hero-lead {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85) !important; /* Light gray */
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    
    .story-hero blockquote {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #ffffff !important; /* White */
        border-left: 3px solid #c9a962; /* Gold */
        padding-left: 24px;
        margin: 40px 0;
    }
    
    /* Story Sections */
    .story-section {
        padding: 80px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    
    .story-section.alt {
        background: var(--dark-surface);
    }
    
    body.theme-light .story-section.alt {
        background: #f8f9fa;
    }
    
    .section-marker {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .story-section h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .story-section h2 em {
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .section-intro {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    
    .story-section p {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .story-section p strong {
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    
    .section-closing {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-top: 40px;
    }
    
    .section-closing.highlight-text {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    /* Etymology / Name Section */
    .etymology {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 24px;
        margin: 48px 0;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .word-block {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px;
        background: var(--dark-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        border-radius: 16px;
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 150px;
    }
    
    body.theme-light .word-block {
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    
    .word-block.highlight {
        border-color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .word-block .word {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    
    .word-block.highlight .word {
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    .word-block .origin {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--text-tertiary);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    
    .word-block p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    .word-connector {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--accent);
    }
    
    /* Equation */
    .equation {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 32px;
        background: var(--dark-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 40px 0;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    body.theme-light .equation {
        background: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    
    .eq-term {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    
    .eq-operator {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    /* Principles */
    .principles {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
        margin: 40px 0;
    }
    
    .principle {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 16px;
    }
    
    .principle i {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1);
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--accent);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    
    .principle p {
        margin: 0;
        padding-top: 8px;
    }
    
    /* Signoff */
    .story-signoff {
        padding: 100px 0;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    
    .signoff-tagline {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    
    .signoff-statement {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto 48px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .signature {
        display: inline-block;
        text-align: left;
    }
    
    .signature-line {
        width: 80px;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
        display: block;
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    
    .signature-title {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-tertiary);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .story-hero {
            padding: 140px 0 60px;
        }
        
        .etymology {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .word-connector {
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }
        
        .equation {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .eq-operator {
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }
    }
</style>
